data.description: Freshly renovated two bedroom, one bath stilt home in the country nestled on 2.27 fenced and cross fenced dry acres with several beautiful mature oak trees. Features real wood cabinets, granite countertops and stainless steel appliances, fresh paint, new floors & fixtures. The underside of the house provides a perfect carport or workshop. It also sets you up with plenty of opportunity for expansion. Enjoy your mornings and evenings on the spacious front porch drinking your coffee or indulging in a night cap.  Located in NW Desoto County with easy access to Hwy 70 & 72 to Bradenton & Sarasota.
